>Minutes</h2>\r\n-------\r\nFrank was a monster who wanted to dance\r\n- what are blocks to creativity?\r\n\r\n\"I can’t\" seems to be a prevalent block for would-be creatives\r\nLynda Berry - helps adults who think they can’t draw\r\n<a href=\"http://www.cbc.ca/radio/q/schedule-for-friday-may-8-2015-1.3065520/cartoonist-lynda-barry-dares-you-to-draw-like-a-kid-1.3065525\" target=\"_blank\">Interview by the CBC</a>\r\n“The Dot”\r\nUse artist theory to disrupt business\r\nNik asks \"Can it be reversed? You have 30 minutes to draw 3 characters\"\r\n<em>Nik will send Andy Warhol article with quote</em>\r\nPeople are currently focused on the end result rather than the experience, geared toward perfection\r\nApple - brand value was the surest way to make a profit over time, decisions prioritized that over immediate profit\r\nExperiencing stigma vs permission to creatively engage in society\r\nBusinesses should create a judgment-free environment where people feel safe\r\nGabor Mate - <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8_j5mmBa4mw\" target=\"_blank\">The Myth of Normal</a>\r\nWho would want to improve their creativity and what is their barrier? Fear?\r\nEveryone - one creative moment per day\r\nFriday at 5:00 pm, stop what you\'re doing and be creative for ten minutes - #FiveTenFriday\r\nSasha: Holly: If you expect people to break their creative barriers, you should break sports barrier etc.\r\n#FailproofFriday\r\nOrin draws Monsters on Monday - <a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/monstersmorning\" target=\"_blank\">#MondayMorningMonsters</a>\r\nCollaborative Sunday Story Time\r\n#FiveTenFriday - \"challenging your creative self\", \"a creative flourish\", \"make the time\"\r\nWhat it could be - the best selfie from a ten minute session, a picture, calligraphy, photograph, arrangement of your food, a poem, a tattoo\r\n10,000 hours to become an expert at something, approach expertise 10 minutes at a time\r\nCan become exceptionally good at something in <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5MgBikgcWnY\" target=\"_blank\">22 hours </a>\r\n\r\n———\r\n\r\nThe Local Tour\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.krisconstable.com/vancouver-vending-machine-circuit/\">Vending Machine Circuit</a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/news/no-fun-city/\">No Fun City</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/VictoriasSecrets/\">Victoria’s Secrets</a>\r\nI know a guy - An app that hooks you up with locals\r\nSell a virtual brochure listing all locations, with or without tour\r\n“Cool doesn’t get destroyed” (dissent among the attendees)\r\nPlug for Nik\'s <a href=\"http://dinnerpartyyvr.com/meals/127-spicy-trouble-in-little-chinatown/ - 3 course, 9-dish dinner for the Battered Women’sSupport Services Association\" target=\"_blank\">Dinner Party YVR</a>\r\nExample of local recommendation - Spicy Beauty, Yunnan food on Kingsway in Vancouver\r\nWhat if you can’t use computers at all, completely word of mouth\r\nFiona R &amp; Kris doing word-of-mouth and postcard only event\r\nSocial network for the elite called - A small world - invite only\r\nIslas Maristas &amp; Tofino are no longer private, discovery of local secrets inevitable\r\n<a href=\"http://rentafriend.com/\">http://rentafriend.com/</a>\r\n\r\n———\r\n\r\npsychoactive drugs are illegal\r\n<a href=\"http://project.cyberpunk.ru/lib/cyberia/cyberia.pdf\">Cyberia - Douglas Rushkoff </a>[PDF download]\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hd1XvmfFYpo\">TJ Dawe - Medicine</a>\r\nMDMA, mushrooms, or LSD camping experience guided by Shaman\r\n<a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Vancouver-Holotropic-Breathwork-Meetup/events/229051045/?rv=me2\">Holotropic Breathwork\r\nDr. Stan Graf’s Holotropic Breathing. (</a><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Vancouver-Holotropic-Breathwork-Meetup/events/229051045/?rv=me2\">Event coming to Vancouver this Saturday</a><a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Vancouver-Holotropic-Breathwork-Meetup/events/229051045/?rv=me2\">)</a>\r\nBilderberg Group type executive retreat\r\n———\r\nReducing Waste in Food Packaging\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.timescolonist.com/news/local/living-without-plastic-tests-mettle-of-victoria-woman-1.872695\">Carol-Lynne Michaels</a>\r\n<a href=\"http://thesoapdispensary.com/\">The Soap Dispensary</a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.zerowastehome.com/\">http://www.zerowastehome.com/</a>\r\nHolly: London Drugs allows you to recycle chocolate bar wrappers\r\nIn our society, we’re OK with the ability to recycle, so we’re not reducing or reusing even though they should be prioritized first (reduce, reuse, recycle)\r\nMembership - to return used and receive sterilized containers\r\nSustainable brands - <a href=\"https://www.dutildenim.com/\">Dutil Denim</a> and <a href=\"https://www.youngliving.com/en_US\" target=\"_blank\">Young Living Deodorant</a>\r\nDIY route to reducing waste- oil pulling with coconut oil toothpaste substitute or tablets of activated charcoal, rinse with apple cider vinegar, if you’re using baking soda to balance the pH\r\nReplace your soap with oils, e.g. avocado oil\r\nOIL FEST: Everything you need to know about oil\r\nStore could also be a venue for sustainability-themed meet-ups\r\n\r\n—\r\n&lt;Insert Seamless Transition Here&gt;\r\nEverything You Need to Know About:\r\nSasha: Pokemon\r\nNik: Tattoo culture, body modification (Holly suggests <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FdXU-Zg9pcM\">The Cultural Heritage of Tattooing | Lars Krutak </a>)\r\nAlanna: Nutrition\r\nAldo: Personal financial management\r\nHolly: Producing events\r\n\r\n—\r\nChecklist of the Best App\r\nExamples of categories: Best restaurants - Canada\r\ncocktails, beer\r\nnightclubs\r\ncoffee shops - with outlets and internet\r\nchocolate, ice cream\r\ndim sum\r\nExamples of lists to check off from: Best of from Georgia Straight\r\n<a href=\"https://www.quiet.ly\" target=\"_blank\">quietly </a>to curate lists','March 7, 2016','','draft','open','open','','','','','2016-03-08 13:26:28','2016-03-08 18:26:28','',0,'htt