>','July 11, 2016','','inherit','closed','closed','','129-revision-v1','','','2016-07-12 02:56:55','2016-07-12 06:56:55','',129,'http://www.ideasmeetings.org/2016/07/129-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(131,1,'2016-07-12 02:57:36','2016-07-12 06:57:36','The Vancouver Chapter usually meets from 7-10pm on Mondays at <a href=\"http://creativecoworkers.com/\">Creative Coworkers</a>.\r\n\r\nWe also have a <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ideasvan\">Facebook Page</a> and often post our events also in the <a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/Vancouver-Tech-Co-Founders/\">Vancouver Pixel Crafters Meetup Group</a>.\r\n\r\nYou don\'t have to have an idea to join us. We\'re a social group who tries to help each other make our ideas happen. You can be any age, ethnicity, and identify as any gender, you just have to be willing to contribute constructively.\r\n<h3>Projects:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://awesomeshitclub.com/\">Awesome Shit Club</a> (Kris, +10 others)</li>\r\n 	<li>Custom Ad Blocker (Kris, Alanna, Nolan)</li>\r\n 	<li>Disruptive Art (Paul, Kris)</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://www.ideasmeetings.org/wiki/Channel_Bonding_project\">Channel Bonding</a> (Clayten, Kiko, Kris)</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://www.ideasmeetings.org/wiki/Biofeedback_sensors\">Biofeedback Sensors</a> (Kris, +10 others)</li>\r\n 	<li>Founders Coffee (Kris, Luke + 4 others - This project has gone offline and is invite only)</li>\r\n 	<li>Dating App/Game/Events (Luke, Kris, Kurtis, Alanna + 3 others)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Minutes:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://www.ideasmeetings.org/2016/07/july-11-2016/\">July 11, 2016</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://www.ideasmeetings.org/2016/06/june-13-2016/\">June 13, 2016</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://www.ideasmeetings.org/2016/06/june-6-2016/\">June 06, 2016</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://www.ideasmeetings.org/2016/05/may-16th-2016/\">May 16, 2016</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://www.ideasmeetings.org/2016/05/may-09-2016/\">May 09